---
title: Camembert and Truffle Hot Pot with Potatoes, Savoy Cabbage and Wild Mushroom Sauce
description: This Vegetable & Camembert Hotpot is bursting full of flavours and make the perfect dinner night option, from HelloFresh. Cook up a fresh start!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vegetable-camembert-hot-pot-e08ce2ea-82a0743b.jpg
